column2:
This game is a good balance between aim, gamesense and ability usage depending on the champion and the role also it is far different from overwatch in terms of gameplay.
let's go to the negatives now: BUGS (lately the dev team have been fixing them)
also we want the play of the game back.

The game itself isnt bad, its a funny game to play with friends or when you dont have anything to do, but if you want something to focus in, i'll list just a little of the game problems, and thats why i wouldnt recommend it now:

- The ranked Matchmaking system is broken, a low elo player can play against a full team of GM and diamonds, wich isnt fun for both parts;
- The Devs dont care too much about the game lately, they just show up skins, battlepasses and sometimes a new champion, They already stated that we'll not have any events this year, so if you played Rise of Furia or something like that and are returning to the game, know that you'll not have anything like that in this year sadly;
- The Att cycle is about 3 months, wich is kinda bad for an online game;
- Some unbalanced champions most of the time didnt even get touched by the devs;
- The Game is full of bugs and server problems, they removed features that they said would fix some bugs but guess what? The bugs still there, the server is at its worse point, a couple of days ago i played a match wich everyone except the tank of my team got stuck on the champion selection screen ( Enemy team included );

These are just some of the problems, if you want to see the real madness come to the discussions session of the game, its a mess, people with login problems, crash problems, lag problems, some people trying to help with the champions balance ( generally the devs doesnt care ), what i have to say is, if you want to come back to the game right now, its not the time, maybe it'll be when Evil Mojo decide that they dont want to kill the game, if you're a new player, maybe you could try it yourself, but dont give huge expectations. If for a miracle the game solve this problems i'll change my review, but for now, thats all folks ;P
(Sorry about my bad english, not a native speaker, hope you guys understand xD)
